        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span> Exclusive community</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#join-now" class="block w-full bg-green-500 text-white py-3 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-green-600">Join Now</a>
